OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's new Police
OL,8,FOmbudsman is to start work tomorrow -
OL,9,Fas politicians across the board warn
OL,10,Fof the challenges she faces.
OL,12,FJacqui Durkin was appointed to the
OL,13,F#173,000-a-year post by the First and
OL,14,FDeputy First Ministers after a seven-
OL,15,Fmonth recruitment process.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FIn a joint statement Michelle O'Neill
OL,8,Fand Emma Little-Pengelly said Ms
OL,9,FDurkin, who was Chief Inspector of
OL,10,FCriminal Justice in Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fsince November 2019, "brings extensive
OL,12,Fsenior leadership experience and a
OL,13,Fstrong track record in oversight,
OL,14,Fgovernance and public service".
OL,16,FJustice Minister Naomi Long welcomed
OL,17,FMs Durkin's appointment, thanking her
OL,18,Ffor the "leadership and expertise" she
OL,19,Fshowed as Chief Inspector.
OL,26,@zD@IOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FShe added: "Jacqui brings a wealth of
OL,8,Fexperience to the role of Police
OL,9,FOmbudsman and I wish her every success
OL,10,Fduring her tenure. The Chief Inspector
OL,11,Fof Criminal Justice in Northern
OL,12,FIreland plays a crucial role in
OL,13,Ffostering improvements throughout the
OL,14,Fjustice sector.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,F"The inspection programme overseen by
OL,8,Fthe Chief Inspector enables us to
OL,9,Fdevelop a more effective and efficient
OL,10,Fcriminal justice system for the people
OL,11,Fof Northern Ireland and Jacqui will
OL,12,Fbring a track record of leadership and
OL,13,Fachievement to her new role."
OL,15,FMLA Doug Beattie welcomed the
OL,16,Fappointment but said there were
OL,17,Fchallenges that need addressed "to
OL,18,Fretain the confidence of the police
OL,19,Frank and file as well as members of
OL,20,Fthe public".
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FThe former UUP leader added: "I have
OL,8,Fworked with Jacqui Durkin since she
OL,9,Fbecame head of the Criminal Justice
OL,10,FInspectorate in 2019 and have always
OL,11,Ffound her to be open, honest, direct,
OL,12,Fand willing to listen. I have no doubt
OL,13,Fshe will bring these qualities to her
OL,14,Fnew role. I hope this appointment
OL,15,Fprovides an opportunity to reset the
OL,16,FPolice Ombudsman's Office and address
OL,17,Fa number of critical challenges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,F"I previously submitted a motion
OL,8,Fcalling on the Justice Minister to
OL,9,Fconduct a review of the Ombudsman's
OL,10,FOffice, setting out a number of
OL,11,Fchanges that I believe are necessary
OL,12,Fto improve its effectiveness. Central
OL,13,Fto this is greater accountability.
OL,14,FThere should be provision for the
OL,15,FOmbudsman to be suspended if they are
OL,16,Fsubject to any form of investigation,
OL,17,Fin line with the Venice Principles, a
OL,18,Fprovision which isn't available at the
OL,19,Fmoment."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FMs Durkin's appointment follows the
OL,8,Fretirement of her predecessor Marie
OL,9,FAnderson. She stepped down months
OL,10,Fafter it emerged she would not face
OL,11,Fcharges arising from a police
OL,12,Finvestigation examining potential
OL,13,Fmisconduct over a domestic incident in
OL,14,F2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FMr Beattie said: "As I wish Jacqui
OL,8,FDurkin well in her tenure, I hope she
OL,9,Fand the Justice Minister will seize
OL,10,Fthis opportunity to reset the
OL,11,FOmbudsman's Office and ensure it is
OL,12,Fequipped to meet the demands placed
OL,13,Fupon it."
OL,26,@uD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,FSDLP Policing Board member Colin
OL,8,FMcGrath MLA said: "Jacqui Durkin has
OL,9,Fhad a distinguished career in the
OL,10,Fcivil service and I welcome her
OL,11,Fappointment as the new Police
OL,12,FOmbudsman. However, the enormous delay
OL,13,Fby the Executive Office in making this
OL,14,Fappointment, at a time when serious
OL,15,Fissues were emerging within the
OL,16,FOmbudsman's Office, tells its own
OL,17,Fstory about how this administration
OL,18,Foperates.
OL,26,@pD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,F"It has taken almost seven months for
OL,8,Fan appointment to be made. When public
OL,9,Fconfidence in an important institution
OL,10,Fis under pressure, that level of delay
OL,11,Fis simply not good enough.
OL,13,F"The Ombudsman's Office now has a
OL,14,Fleadership team that includes former
OL,15,Fcivil service and policing experience.
OL,16,FThat makes it all the more important
OL,17,Fthat the organisation demonstrates
OL,18,Fcomplete independence in its work.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782479949
OL,3,CDurkin lands #173k-a-year Ombudsman
OL,4,Crole as politicians warn of challenges
OL,5,Cahead
OL,7,F"The challenge now is to restore
OL,8,Fconfidence, strengthen accountability
OL,9,Fand ensure the Ombudsman's Office is
OL,10,Fonce again recognised as a robust,
OL,11,Findependent watchdog acting in the
OL,12,Fpublic interest."
